      <elementaryExchange id="df126486-77ab-5add-ac28-c67b60cd6369" unitId="487df68b-4994-4027-8fdc-a4dc298257b7" casNumber="000123-51-3" amount="0.0034202" elementaryExchangeId="6abb5a34-7f0b-4a9a-8452-211a0ebee04d" formula="C5H12O">
        <name xml:lang="en">3-Methyl-1-butanol</name>
        <unitName xml:lang="en">kg</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">Estimation.  The remaining amount of unreacted 3-methyl-1-butanol (4.8 % of the input) was assumed to leave the production process with the waste water. Furthermore, it was assumed that this waste water is treated in a internal waste water plant. The removal efficiency for 3-methyl-1-butanol was assumed to be 90%. 

It is assumed that the manufacturing plants are located in an urban/industrial area and consequently the emissions are categorised as emanating in a high population density area. 

The emissions into water are assumed to be emitted into rivers.</comment>
